### Overview
The Student Registration System will be used by a local college to register students for courses and also for students to self-register. The program was built using Java libraries in a TextPad editor. 

### Screens
A few screens were designed for the user to be able to initiate and complete the registration process:
    Login Screen
    Create Account Screen
    Course Registration Screen
    Profile Screen
    Navigation Option Screen
